ote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隊波入座率有冇5成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n降班果場爆左人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多人睇住都打得咁差<br />\n護級最尾嗰場，人哋都放粒比你，都要倒輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d4c78b97e6b0c058f00c0ccaacfb2882d03cf3","tid":264873,"uid":77342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"踢丙組嘅東方都可以踢亞冠啦，有咩咁出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2894413ec7b9107f1eeb20c3fdf291ddc61990b4","tid":264873,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}